  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
    <a href="/book" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all hover:scale-105" style="background-color: var(--accent-color); color: #000;">
      <span class="material-icons text-base">calendar_today</span>
